{"tid":951207,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"聯儲局無視警告 彭博︰特朗普想炒掉鮑威爾","createTime":"2018-12-22T07:01:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-23T07:36:03.000Z","uid":66271,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"252032fe21fdc12cc57e3d90820045158363efb5","tid":951207,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T07:01:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181222/large/1545457392_1ab3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181222%2Flarge%2F1545457392_1ab3.jpg&h=e797963a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181222/59058831\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181222%2F59058831&d=ZH4yc4t%2FNb3Zc6B%2FQrMq50zHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=31e230ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181222%2F59058831&h=18e6558b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181222/59058831</a><br />\n<br />\n美國聯儲局上周宣佈加息四分一厘，上調至2.25厘至2.5厘，為今年第四次加息。美國總統特朗普早已多次警告聯儲局主席鮑威爾(Jerome Powell)不要加息，以免阻礙美國經濟增速。可是，聯儲局無視總統，維持市場預期的加息，這已觸怒了特朗普，彭博引述四名知情人士指，特朗普在宣佈加息後已多次討論過想炒掉鮑威爾。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，特朗普身邊的顧問警告，如真的炒掉鮑威爾將會是一次「災難性」(disastrous)舉動，他們寄望特朗普能在聖誕假期間消氣，可是特朗普近日仍不斷討論要炒掉鮑威爾。<br />\n美國總統炒聯儲局主席或會帶來毀滅性的漣漪效應，影響市場信心，因為聯儲局不能在免受政治壓力下領導美國經濟，大大影響其獨立性。事實上，根據美國《聯邦儲備法》，總統有權在合理理由下炒聯儲局主席，可是法律上仍有爭議。前美國總統卡特(Jimmy Carter)就曾在1979年，將聯儲局主席米勒（William Miller）調任財政部長。"},{"pid":"6e36aaaa0b5837bf7e7a76ecd701f6c035b11ca5","tid":951207,"uid":17429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T07:01:27.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"b1334d75cc5f12660d9b44807f77f43e78874255","tid":951207,"uid":208376,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T07:02:59.000Z","msg":"搞fed想命都唔要？<img src=\